<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="boring-adj">boring <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'bɔːrɪŋ/    美 /'bɔːrɪŋ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>无聊的；令人厌烦的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>dead boring</strong> job 
无聊透顶的工作</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They say it’s boring to hear the same songs all the time.
他们说总是听相同的歌曲令人感到厌烦。</p><footer>2010 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Mr Smith, <strong><em>_</em></strong><em> (tire) of the <strong><em>_</em></strong></em> (bore) speech, started to read a novel.  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. tired; boring  </p></div>